In the current video data analysis project, I solved the problem of classifying objects using neural networks. Developed a complete set of tools necessary for training neural networks, as well as a library that allows using of neural networks. (Torch/Lua, C++, CUDA, OpenMP,  Python(numpy,scipy,scikit), convolutional neural networks)I am the lead developer of the next video data analysis project.
